    <briefdescription>
<para>Multi-segment waveform composer (Phase B). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Sequences a list of segments — each one a <computeroutput>synth</computeroutput> configuration plus an on-time and a trailing off-time gap — into a single IQ stream, optionally repeating the whole sequence or running forever. The composer owns one <computeroutput>synth</computeroutput> at a time (the active segment) and reuses the Phase-A engine verbatim, so every waveform type / SNR mode / MLS behaviour is identical to the single-waveform path; a one-segment spec is byte-identical to calling <computeroutput>synth</computeroutput> directly.</para>
<para>Lifecycle: wfm_compose_create -&gt; wfm_compose_execute* -&gt; wfm_compose_destroy</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structwfm__segment__t" kindref="compound">wfm_segment_t</ref><sp/>segs[2]<sp/>=<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>{.type<sp/>=<sp/>0,<sp/>.fs<sp/>=<sp/>1e6,<sp/>.freq<sp/>=<sp/>1e5,<sp/>.snr<sp/>=<sp/>100.0,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.num_samples<sp/>=<sp/>1000,<sp/>.off_samples<sp/>=<sp/>500},<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>tone,<sp/>then<sp/>a<sp/>gap</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>{.type<sp/>=<sp/>4,<sp/>.fs<sp/>=<sp/>1e6,<sp/>.sps<sp/>=<sp/>8,<sp/>.snr<sp/>=<sp/>9.0,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.num_samples<sp/>=<sp/>4096,<sp/>.off_samples<sp/>=<sp/>0},<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>qpsk</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="wfm__compose_8h_1afe1a8932740c4aeef2ddc75968d9273f" kindref="member">wfm_compose_state_t</ref><sp/>*c<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="wfm__compose_8h_1ab04a3451d1136dc4b562670be071150b" kindref="member">wfm_compose_create</ref>(segs,<sp/>2,<sp/>0,<sp/>0);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">float</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>complex<sp/>buf[4096];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">size_t</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>n;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">while</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>((n<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="wfm__compose_8h_1adff237dc82f2ca7e0d5c1d04060d33a6" kindref="member">wfm_compose_execute</ref>(c,<sp/>buf,<sp/>4096))<sp/>&gt;<sp/>0)<sp/>{<sp/>...<sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="wfm__compose_8h_1a076cf6ddf7028af2929b0da72eaeabf6" kindref="member">wfm_compose_destroy</ref>(c);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
